
##### Steps on working for Solar System using Sprites:

First Step, Please make sure you include, p5.play.js in the index.html
Then, create Sprites for each of my planets at various positions, you can do at random positions also.
Syntax: var planetname = createSprites(x,y,width,height);

Then load the image,
Syntax, create a function preload and then load all my images,
function preload(){
planetimage = loadImage("path of image");
}

Then add the needed image,
Syntax: planetname.addImage("planet1",imagename);

Next Step, add collide condition on my platents and if collide happens them planet is destroyed, asjust the collide using set collider,
Syntax,
sun.collide(planet name);
sun.setCollider("shape",xoff,yoff,radius.width,height);

also for every certain frame update the size if my sun.

Syntax: if(frameCount%10 ===0){
sun.scale=sun.scale+0.1;
}
